wikipedia_page.main: Alexander Tulloch MacQueen (born 30 November 1973) is an English actor. He has appeared on television, film and radio in the UK in productions such as Holby City,  Doctor Who, Hut 33, Peep Show, The Thick of It, Keeping Mum, and The Inbetweeners.  He also guest-starred in The Durrells in Series 4.
